    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 V8 era. This vehicle maintains factory-spec tolerances, featuring flawlessly linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The induction note from the individual throttle bodies remains crisp, complemented by a lightning-fast M-DCT transmission that executes gear changes with surgical precision. Chassis dynamics are uncompromised; the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides immediate feedback without any hydraulic degradation. Every bushing, link, and subframe mount exhibits zero play, ensuring the limited-slip differential translates every bit of torque to the tarmac. Cosmetically, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory matte finish with negligible bolster wear. This is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
