      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible, mint condition that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014no scratches, no dents, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell. It drives like a total dream and has been kept tucked away safely in a garage. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself how gorgeous it is. Let's chat!",
